{
  "texts": [
    "In cases of disagreement, a third reviewer, NY, served as a tiebreaker to reach a consensus.",
    "Meta-analysis was conducted utilizing a random effects model, and the I² statistic was applied to assess the heterogeneity among individual studies.",
    "To evaluate potential publication bias, funnel plots were generated.",
    "The analysis was carried out using the \"Comprehensive Meta Analysis v. 4\" software.",
    "This study compared AI-augmented LVO detection and non-AI in various patient processing times for emergent endovascular therapy in acute ischemic strokes."
  ]
}